Sources used......video was vobs off ELEKTRI4KA and new audio source of Fresh ....many thanks both :)

Right work done.....firstly took the vobs we had and made a script to crop it, resize, white balance, brightness and contrast. Then dropped that into vdub and used some more filters ... inc rgb eq, smoother, sharpen, hue, intes and a few more.

Now the audio was some pretty good cam audio, but needed to be cut and synced and then filtered some. One done it was a case of muxing together and packing it up.
